    ["6949f08480831a003d6c4afa"] = {
        ["EndTimestamp"] = 1768874400,
        ["Title"] = "【委托密函】刻舟委托密函轮换说明",
        ["Content"] = {
            [1] = {
                ["language"] = "CN",
                ["title"] = "【委托密函】刻舟委托密函轮换说明",
                ["body"] = "<p><img src=\"http://pan01-cdn-dna-ali.shyxhy.com/upload/728x200_密函轮换预告_刻舟.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"728\" height=\"200\"></p>\n<div data-page-id=\"OsvSdmWa0olwrDxuQlPcpdrwnSh\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-docx-has-block-data=\"false\">\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-AjajdoBh3o2LqoxY3Npc1Lkbnyd\">委托密函将于2026年1月20日 更新后进行轮换，以下为轮换规则。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-WkMMdb0TGodOStxfS8QcEH5antc\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-GwS0dWbJPoB2H1xaQRZc740inig\">2026年1月20日 更新后：</div>\n<ul class=\"list-bullet1\">\n<li class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-QRiWdBVLhov0AsxQTVTcR2vxnLc\" data-list=\"bullet\">\n<div><span style=\"color: rgb(78, 147, 243);\"><strong>「密函：刻舟」「密函：若华的飞光」</strong></span><strong>将替换</strong><span style=\"color: rgb(78, 147, 243);\"><strong>「密函：扶疏」「密函：泽世的慈雨」</strong></span>进入沉浸式戏剧的限时奖励中。</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Lv8OdqSKCoEtTExuOp8cumUVnpg\" data-list=\"bullet\">\n<div><span style=\"color: rgb(78, 147, 243);\"><strong>「密函：扶疏」</strong></span>将替换<strong><span style=\"color: rgb(218, 42, 74);\">「密函：黎瑟」</span></strong>加入梦魇残声挑战奖励中；</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-JTAwdTxLQoP43yxrN0ecXViGnzg\" data-list=\"bullet\">\n<div><span style=\"color: rgb(78, 147, 243);\"><strong>「密函：泽世的慈雨」</strong></span>将替换<span style=\"color: rgb(218, 42, 74);\"><strong>「密函：放逐怒雷」</strong></span>加入梦魇残声挑战奖励中；</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-HIvsdDW31oVlajxSkyJco0Ebn8b\" data-list=\"bullet\">\n<div><span style=\"color: rgb(78, 147, 243);\"><strong>「密函：未来之鸽」</strong></span>将替换<span style=\"color: rgb(218, 42, 74);\"><strong>「密函：春玦戟」</strong></span>加入梦魇残声挑战奖励中；</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-TlDJdc8UVoqfeexJB5TcQq2lnRQ\" data-list=\"bullet\">\n<div><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(218, 42, 74);\">「密函：黎瑟」「密函：放逐怒雷」「密函：春玦戟」</span></strong>将永久加入【委托密函】商店兑换中。</div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-O6afdtBZPowR7nxpEfqc5H1onzz\">特别提醒：本次梦魇残声奖励轮换时间为1月20日（周二），更新后<strong>不会重置</strong>梦魇残声周奖励次数，若想获取<span style=\"color: rgb(78, 147, 243);\"><strong>「密函：扶疏」「密函：泽世的慈雨」「密函：未来之鸽」</strong></span>的狩月人，请根据自身需求安排游玩挑战。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-CTicdHXVlovl1TxjMFPcxTdPnnb\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-ZKRRdAfTooQV1Kx3lQ8c7c6snsg\">随着本次沉浸式戏剧更新，剧目中的【舞台伴奏】与【推荐属性】也会一同进行更新。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-YPKhdp70Vo6ZQ0xiJoFcx1tfnqg\">本期推荐属性：<span style=\"color: rgb(78, 147, 243);\">水属性</span>、<span style=\"color: rgb(248, 153, 52);\">光属性</span></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-RBP4dCUwCo23glx6JfScwYncnch\">本期【舞台伴奏】将会轮换一批新的&ldquo;伴奏&rdquo;，以下为【不朽剧目】中部分&ldquo;伴奏&rdquo;：</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-ORvPdzDDAo8VskxRVixc4AI5n2g\">● 【抉择变奏：水与光之歌】敌方单位受到的水属性及光属性伤害提高400%，受到的其他属性伤害降低50%。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-WcIGdEsBtotCAGxCdHwcZtovnxc\">● 【活跃急板：狩猎巨人】友方单位生命值百分比大于80.0%时，技能威力提高100%，受到伤害时不会产生僵直。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-KBV7d4rVwoe3w9xjOsjc727bnse\">● 【激昂行板：壮士决】执行近战攻击后，获得造成的武器伤害提高10.0%效果，持续10秒，最多叠加5层，满层时，受到伤害时不会产生僵直。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-EP35dY9vEooexoxCsTwc7APJneb\">● 【防御变奏：持续洗礼】敌方单位受到的伤害降低60.0%，每次受到持续伤害时，伤害降低幅度降低6.0%。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-V7Vmd5OWeoi5r3xlz1Dcxo7ynUg\">● 【协调柔板：无命毒师】友方单位暴击伤害降低100%，造成的持续伤害提高50.0%。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-VKRid8APKoMYj5x9QVmcmNgPnef\">*更多【舞台伴奏】可在版本更新后进入游戏内查看。</div>\n</div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>",
                ["title1"] = "【委托密函】刻舟委托密函轮换说明",
            },
        },
