    ["694d334a699ac453a51ae222"] = {
        ["EndTimestamp"] = 1768795200,
        ["Title"] = "【皎皎特别剧场】活动说明",
        ["Content"] = {
            [1] = {
                ["language"] = "CN",
                ["title"] = "【皎皎特别剧场】活动说明",
                ["body"] = "<p><img src=\"http://pan01-cdn-dna-ali.shyxhy.com/upload/728x200_皎皎特别剧场.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"728\" height=\"200\"></p>\n<div data-page-id=\"LkTbdAKlkoqmDBxSSSkcJmoKnSc\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-docx-has-block-data=\"false\">\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-ZJlZd0xy5oS07jxf7rGck5Yznwe\">银烛狂欢节在一连串意外中结束后，冰湖城又笼罩了一层阴云。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-QIKNdJTYJo1bBOxU6Y7cs88rnAh\">在这个不大不小的危急时刻，那位自称光之魔王的皎皎站了出来！</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnmzPKZHSfDnWocPBCepAM8b\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnD0Lq6P0estBAoUT16OB7th\"><strong>【活动时间】</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnOK0Wskaeg2bFMVcn83tH8b\">2025年12月25日 10:00 ~ 2026年1月20日 05:00 （UTC+8）</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnKoFLTXyccV6rCMK6ncNLgf\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnsoIRaWvWPU3EsS4kh16z7j\"><strong>【开放条件】</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcndnLJH8z57Z61PZe2ReHS4e\">完成限时活动任务世界纪游【皎皎特别剧场】。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnIjOlwj3Lw1RaJ9GKB9UtVd\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcniZ1cssjonlIlMZgdJwjxN4\"><strong>【奖励内容】</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnK0xII7eWLFOh6SOSeiRvZf\">「委托密函线索」「暮夜的履迹」「战斗旋律&middot;三」「深红凝珠」「皎皎之民的信物」「铜币」</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcn4L8JEPZkEtb8UU9WZzrumh\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnSPqL6vXbzYv7yYjG2z5S3c\"><strong>【皎皎特别剧场活动规则】</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnqJJPVZl8PC9U6RA3U74EQ4\">完成任务&ldquo;皎皎特别剧场&rdquo;后，可在盖雷亚剧院的普奇团长处报名参加活动。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-XEqJdcd1HoSNIBxHYLJcEpjrnQf\">在皎谊舞会中，跟随舞台上皎皎的指示，展示对应的魔灵和展示动作完成匹配，可获得奖励。展示同种类型的魔灵即可完成匹配，释放&ldquo;奇迹你好箱&rdquo;的技能可以完成闪亮你好箱和锐意你好箱的匹配。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-XG2idkkQGoY719xjRmwcy1cpnDP\">在每次皎谊舞会中，完成一次及以上的匹配，舞会结束时可以获得高级奖励；每个账号在活动期间最多获得5次高级奖励，之后即使完成多次匹配，也仅能获得普通奖励。两次皎谊舞会的间隔为半个小时。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-TF9YdpeovoSRquxw18XczKZSnfn\">在欢聚一时中，交付素材达到一定进度后，会获得奖励。奖励将通过全服邮件发送。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-YsAtdmpbjoRKQ0xut9xcTJiVnKg\">在欢聚一时中，点击【自动添加】会依照材料品质自动加入可交付素材。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-JyV1dpgBTo0OQNxnzOMcreQRnMs\">在欢聚一时中，素材交付已完成所有进度后，【自动添加】不再可用，但仍然可以手动添加并交付素材,完成任务并获取奖励。</div>\n</div>",
                ["title1"] = "【皎皎特别剧场】活动说明",
            },
        },
