        ["Title"] = "【沉浸式戏剧】参演热映剧目，领取扶疏委托",
        ["Content"] = {
            [1] = {
                ["language"] = "CN",
                ["title"] = "【沉浸式戏剧】参演热映剧目，领取扶疏委托密函",
                ["body"] = "<p><img src=\"http://pan01-cdn-dna-ali.shyxhy.com/upload/728x200_沉浸式戏剧_简1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"720\" height=\"200\"></p>\n<div data-page-id=\"R4eVdOGM5oPIvlxedxNcTG6vnRc\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-docx-has-block-data=\"false\">\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnZzH4RU9SG1U2Z7fSp9loQb\">沉浸式戏剧已开启，踏上舞台，演绎属于你的剧目。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnpQhlezj3e7AFmFsYjkbTdv\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnfvB5G2U14qGOOgakVCPPzY\"><strong>【开启条件】</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnXosaQK8kA2onv5r6J14etg\">完成泊暮篇剧情【审判日】与特殊支线任务【全新戏剧】。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnRHSJAdQIicZASlWQFOYwZV\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnonW6C0q2d0Z4tuaI4GaHGg\"><strong>【本期时间】</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnGX9RASNGS3eFV59Uo0ir6e\">2025年12月23日开服后 ~ 2026年1月20日 10:00 （UTC+8）</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnhhfLcHJRvEs7JYsWzwS77g\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnMF7aarzvAuF7fqP0NTtNic\"><strong>【本期奖励内容】</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnp2pjoxoZ4ZTfvzVf4DlsMc\"><span style=\"color: rgb(78, 147, 243);\"><strong>「密函：扶疏」「密函：泽世的慈雨」</strong></span>「委托密函线索」「养成材料」「魔之楔」「铜币」等。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnk7p0FYntVjXiyuVRMruldg\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcn2LUQgVyGw8OkvCH1cY0HDc\"><strong>【限时奖励说明】</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnKvcyJNsVakbL2kwhFoF3jc\"><span style=\"color: rgb(78, 147, 243);\"><strong>「密函：扶疏」「密函：泽世的慈雨」</strong></span>为本期限时奖励，本期结束后将替换为<span style=\"color: rgb(78, 147, 243);\"><strong>「</strong><strong>密函：刻舟」「密函：若华的飞光」</strong>。</span></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnvI5y0wOKyMtuSI64biAlFb\"><span style=\"color: rgb(78, 147, 243);\"><strong>「密函：扶疏」</strong></span>可通过达成本期【热映剧目】与【不朽剧目】的星级获得。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnVFmNGmFhNmCINhmiEUQfkd\"><span style=\"color: rgb(78, 147, 243);\"><strong>「密函：泽世的慈雨」</strong></span>可在本期【观剧纪念】商店中使用「剧目票根」兑换获得。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnkfidytUOLrbUsYu17ldoTd\">在本期【沉浸式戏剧】结束后，<span style=\"color: rgb(78, 147, 243);\"><strong>「密函：扶疏」「密函：泽世的慈雨」</strong></span>将替换加入【梦魇残声】每周挑战的挑战奖励中。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcn5g509O5YX8fPSr4hWADqzg\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnQZ2dfWkDB9QmvZvarIsLr6\"><strong>【玩法说明】</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnM55OdqX4nxbNV6QbMqFUIb\">&bull; 沉浸式戏剧分为【经典剧目】、【热映剧目】与【不朽剧目】三部分。需完成前一剧目，才能解锁下一剧目。其中【热映剧目】和【不朽剧目】会随版本更新轮换，【不朽剧目】开放永续关卡，满足条件即可无限挑战。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnxxsjKR6wNAAVaD8h4jO4ic\">&bull; 在限定时间内击败关卡内所有敌人即算完成挑战，在每个剧目下，伴随通关都将获得一定的星数和「票根」，狩月人可在奖励列表领取星数奖励，并在观剧纪念商店兑换心仪的物品。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnipIdDUCPnf2iZV4XXXAfFg\">&bull; 【经典剧目】与【热映剧目】包含【勇者征程】与【勇者归途】两轮战斗，需分别使用不同的角色配队出战，最终以两轮战斗获得的总星数结算奖励。不朽剧目仅有【勇者征程】一轮战斗。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcniPZBGQlI34oHCdOECz2kWd\">&bull; 每轮战斗分为5个房间，需逐层推进。通关当前层【勇者征程】【勇者归途】两轮的全部房间后，才可解锁下一幕关卡。超时或未击败当前房间的目标，都将无法进入下一房间。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnLoyNf574ZQIonDsgCVZYz5\">&bull; 所有关卡附带【舞台伴奏】效果，提供战斗中增益/减益Buff，需根据效果调整策略。</div>\n</div>",
